    "To this end, a platform must be established for organizing different component models via APIs.",
    "This platform can conduct system-wide inferences by intelligently combining the inferences from various component models in DTN.",
    "Specifically, the platform can be built on large base models by leveraging their ability to merge knowledge from different fields.",
    "Such a platform can also prompt AI agents to collaborate effectively to achieve network performance goals.",
    "The agent can gain knowledge by applying supervised learning and reinforcement learning (RL)."
